flowchart TD
    A[Start Bootstrap] --> B[Initiator validates tranche preamble]
    B --> C[Initiator creates tranche substrate<br/>tranche-preamble.md, decor.md, decor-updates/, ticket-map.md, session-logs/, replay-traces/]
    C --> D[Initiator generates envelopes:<br/>Documentation Envelope<br/>Initial DECOR Envelope (decor.md placeholder)<br/>Ticket Map Skeleton]
    D --> E[Initiator validates templates and metadata<br/>naming, namespace, identity roots]
    E --> F[Initiator registers tranche in project index]
    F --> G[Orchestrator reviews bootstrap state<br/>checks folders, envelopes, metadata, templates]
    G --> H{Bootstrap complete?}
    H -- No --> I[Surface bootstrap drift<br/>Initiator corrects<br/>repeat validation]
    I --> G
    H -- Yes --> J[Bootstrap complete<br/>Lifecycle moves to Interpretation Phase]
    J --> K[End Bootstrap]
